location.fullValue: Trillium IV A Plan, Adley Oaks

data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home on a spacious corner lot in Evangeline Heights. Interior features include tray ceilings, tile throughout main living area, vinyl plank in bedroom, tankless water heater, and a spacious laundry room with custom sliding barn door and custom dog kennel. The exterior features a double carport, attached storage, shed, and storm shutters. An additional cement slab was placed behind carport for a patio to be added.  Roof replaced in 2021. Currently flood zone A, a FEMA letter of map amendment is pending to remove from flood zone.
